            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Saluti <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustae</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>dendrophori <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustales</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>consistentes <abbr>Med</abbr> <lb n="4"/>it<expan><ex>em</ex><abbr>q</abbr><ex>ue</ex></expan> Nidae sc<expan><ex>h</ex><abbr>olam</abbr></expan> <lb n="5"/>de suo fecerunt <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>loc</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>adsig</abbr><ex>nato</ex></expan> a <expan><abbr>vic</abbr><ex>anis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Nide</abbr><ex>nsibus</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>3 aneinanderpassende Fragmente. Spuren von roter Farbe in den Buchstaben. Z. 4 (Anfang): Buchstabe I steht anstelle eines getilgten C. (B): AE 1962; Liertz: Z. 1: Salu[ti]; Liertz: Z. 6: Nid(ensibus).</p>
            </div>
